				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: finaly have fade now what?<a name="70884"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 11 04 2:29 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Remove the message to your group.  It takes time (less than a second to a second, but still, that can kill you when you really need Fade to save your arse fast).  I never bother telling people I've fading unless I'm working a pull where someone is tagging.  Otherwise, the group doesn't much care so long as the mobs come in the right quantities.  If you really want something on line 2, try /stopsong.
<br />

<br />
Calli</span></td>
