				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: finaly have fade now what?<a name="70901"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 11 04 2:28 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I have two fade hotkeys. One that does /stopsong and one that doesn't. The second is handy in corpse dragging runs and other times when you need an extended invis. Start selos and fade. Selos will keep pulsing and you can run around invis'ed.
<br />

<br />
Putting a message to inform your group as the last line is a good idea. It stops the MT from tagging the mob he sees, because he doesn't know you're trying to abort the pull until the rest of them come around the corner.</span></td>
