				<td colspan="2"><span>I always have a group message for my fade.  It lets your healer know it's safe to heal you.
<br />

<br />
This most important thing for fade is knowing exactly where your hotkey is stored.  I have no room on my front page of hotkeys (7 songs + 3 slots for instrument swapping).
<br />

<br />
I recommend putting it on page 3 in your 3rd slot.  That way to activate it, you just hit shift-3, then 3.  If you move with WSAD.  it's VERY fast.  you definatly dont want to be wasting valuable time hunting down the hotkey with your mouse.</span></td>
