<br />

<br />
/stopsong
<br />
/cast 1
<br />

<br />
hotkeys.  So it does bind my song slots to my hotkey bank.  I also keep 1 hand on the mouse at all times so I only have my left hand free for movement and twisting.  It lets me play like a FPS.  I cant even begin to explain how much this helps with pulling.
<br />

<br />
Oh, another cool fade trick is on CR.  Start playing selos, then fade.  Selos will keep playing indefinatly and you will still be invis for corpse dragging etc.</span></td>
