				<td colspan="2"><span>Now that you have fade, you need to group and use it to pull with.  Practice up.
<br />

<br />
I have no messages or macros...just a hotkey with fade.  If a song is running, fade still works.  Stopsong is not rquired unless you are singing one and it lands after you have fadded.  (for me this means the odd click to get an inprogress song to stop)  If it has landed then fade will work.  Like above, just do not do anything that would break invis if it were cast on you.
